Its scary how easy it would be to just end it all...A jump off a bidge...a rope around the neck...a knife in the right place...so many ways, all so easy...

However, the easy way out is almost never the best way...suiside is a selfish path that the selfcentered and the cowerdly take...I have so many options...yet time is short...Of all the things out there, only a few of them acually seem possible...I want to do this and that, and yet when ever I try, things come up...Life is not an easy thing...and nothing is ever as easy as it seems. So much...and no one to help...

Lonlyness...every one exspiriences it...more so then others...so many times where things would be so much easier if some one would stay with me...If just one person would tell me that I'm inportant...to some how prove to me that I am not just another person who is just going to live a pointless existance and die at the end of it all...

What is life...why are we here? Is there any real reason? For once, I would like to know the truth about something...I hate all the lieing, all the trickery, but it never ends. Is there something that is out there that has a purpose? Why the hell are we here? Why does God exist? Why does existance exist? Why is time time? Why why why why why! I know I will never know these things, but I can't stop thinking about them. I'm at the verge of insanity, all becuase of the unanswerable. I can't explain it, I'm too big a thinker. I look at the picture bigger then the big picture, and I can't find any answer. Why! Why can't thingsbe easyer. Why do people find such trivial knowledge so important? Why would a carpenter need to know how to program a computer? Why would a writer need to lean about every minor detail of the history of the world? Why can I never get answers to the simpliest of questions!

I...I can't understand myself...even as I write this very post, I don't see how it has any bearing on life. How will this help me in the future? How will my complaining and insane ranting help the world? Why do I sit infront of a laptop, writeing every thing that comes out of my head. Why can't thinks just make sence? There si too much confusion in the world, too many problems. Nothing is easy, nothing ever has been and nothing ever will be. It is hard to be good, hard to be bad, hard to stay in the middle. Hell, its hard just getting through each day with out going insane. I don't know what to do or where to go, I don't know how to do what I need. I can't find the answers that I so long for. I need help, and yet there is no one around. Why can't I just find some one that will help me, why can't I complete the important things. Why can't I do what I need to do. Why is the world so damn complicated!

I type and type, and yet I can't find any reason for any of it. I don't understand why I'm doing this, and I don't understand why I continue living. Why does the body stay together? Why are molicules what they hard? WHy do things exist. Is God has no beginning and no end, why does he exist? What if god just didn't...What if he never was. Nothing would be. Finally, an answer...but the only thing it does is lead to more questions. The world is full of questions. I need an escape...I need a way to clear my mind, to empty all that is in it...Not even typeing is doing that...I need a way out. I need to find the window that God opened for me, I need to find the right path. I...I need something...

And I just lost my steam...I only have one more question...why?

Damn, does it feel good to be out of that emotional ditch...Though, a lot of people here probably didn't know I was in one...I wonder if I'm really that emotionally dead in real life...Anyways, lots of things are clearing up, I have a good Idea of where I want to go to collage, and I have a lot of things worked out...damn, I never knew I could be this in control of my life...I feel so good right now, and sunday should be a very good day at work...Heh, thats one of the things changing...hopefully anyways...I will be around and feeling a lot better, getting some writing done and such...Oh, and Andy, about the story you looked over, there are somethings I need to point out when I see you again. One I can say right now, its not finished. Until later, every one.

This world is full of odd surprizes and amazeing expiriences. One must find a reason for anything, and yet there is always a reason against it. I look out apone the world with open eyes and a searching mind, looking for all that need to be found. Things which lerk in the shadows call my name, and things which bath in the light hide from me. I am not eveil, just misunderstood. Come, oh those of the forgotten. Come and heal the world from its tortured state.


When I just sit down a write, strange things come out. I know not from where they come or even how then come, they just do. All I need is inspiration, and wonderous things can occor...

"To open you eyes to a new veiw is like opening a closed door. Even if you 'know' whats back there, you can never really be sure."

I find it a bit humorous when I see people years older then me dealing with the same problems that people my age face...and yet they still look at me like I'm some naive teenager that knows nothing about life...Hmm...I should think more on this...

I am starting to get back in the writing mood...by the look of things, I might have my Mafia story done but the end of the mounth...Thats a hopeful thought...Ah well, we will see how things work out...I need to organize my thoughts...

Again, I think back to simpler times...when I didn't care about girls, when I read more then a man locked in a libray...When I actually was cared for...People think that a few words will change how I look of life...Seems like I'm not the naive one in this shoe box...

Gay people really piss me off...


Ok, So I was at work today, and it was rather good. I got to my break ok (Which was moved from 5 to 3, Thanks Matt...) And I sit down with my friends...One is gay and was eating with his boyfriend...We start talking...And they start talking about what happened at 2:00 AM this morning and how every one knew about it...I knew what they were talking about, but I played dumb so that the subject would change and I could stay out of the whole damned thing...It didn't work...You can probably guess what it was the "happened"...The one which wasn't my friend more or less shouted it out at me...I left...I stood up, finished my drink, and threw my trash away, walking out, shaking my head, and kind of laughing to my self...I could have torn the building down, I was so flipping angry...I got out side and sat down, getting freash air and trying to lose the mental piture that that gave me...I felt sick to my stumic and walked around a bit...I then went to the wall and closed my eyes, relaxing myself the way I do it...I would have smashed ether of the two of them's face in if they came out to talk with me...probably curse them out as well...And I'm not one to do any of those things, especially in public...The point is, people just don't know when to drop a subject...My friend assured me it would never happen again...And I belive him...good friend, bad sexual tastes...Anyways, that was my day...Until later...

Happy Easter!


If you can call it that...I sure hope it happy for all of you, seem I'll be having a rather lonely easter...I'm here at my sister's house, but she is going to be my only "family" and I'm starting to consider her at the same position as I consider my borther-in-law...I'm going to be here with her, my brother-in-law, their kids, my brother-in-law's parents and grandmom, and none of my true family...infact, my true family isn't even getting together for easter...I don't know what the hell they all are thinking...I find Easter to be the most important day in the year, even more important then christmas...And yet I'm going to spend it cleaning and being online on my laptop in the back room...I don't belong here...I have no way of contacting my family and no way of really enjoying this day...I'll be on City of Heroes for most of it, but thats as close I'm going to come...Damn this world...I don't see why I even try...One of these days, I will finally see that its hopeless...Then I don't know whats going to happen...Things are going to have to change with me, or my end is going to be soon...Thats all for now...Like I said, I hope all of you are having a better day...

I have found that I one, scare people, and two, cause a sence of untusting...I don't know what it is about me, but for some odd reason, I can never be right and I can't keep my word...I have a strange way about myself that people just don't get, and so are scared...I feel sorry for the people that just pass me off as a young stupid teenager, becuase I am a hell of alot more...I also don't understand why people don't seem to like to tell me thier problems...I usually have to ask whats wrong and convince the person that I want to listen, or else they just brush me aside...I try and be nice, I try and help every one, and yet people seem to hate me...I need to get out...I need to go somewhere that I'm wanted...some where where I can belong...this isn't it, becuase people don't want me to belong...I shouldn't have put this down though...people are going to think something is wrong with me...damn, and I'm too lazy to spell cheak...ah, screw it, I don't give a damn right now...

So yeah, went and saw a movie with an old friened, it was alot of fun...Other then that, it was rather un eventful...


Today isn't going very good...I was too tired and didn't really get up till about 10:30...Then I found out that Luke's backpack was left in the van and he can't go to school...Oi, I hope nothing else goes wrong...


Anyways, things should be looking up...For any one else that I havn't told, I got my laptop about a week ago...School is going good, things are coming in nicely...My grades are good...Yeah, my life is really boring...Anyways, talk to you later...
Wow...havn't posted in a while...

Yeah...its the week of christmas...yippy...

On a side note, it would seem people don't know me like I think they do...When ever I start talking about how the world is screwed, they start talking to me about why I'm so angry at myself...I appreciate the concern, but get your focus strait. My last post was something about how my life has no reason or some such nonsense. Now, I didn't say this because I'm going to go out and kill my self, I said this because it seems like no one really cares. I write a good paper, I get "good job, now do this one" which pisses me off. I finish a hard test and get "way to go, here's another one". So yeah, no one really cares about how I feel or what I'm doing. I was one the internet last night, and I was trying to get some stuff done. Suddenly the connection's lost and I can get it back. Turns out my parents had packed the modem away for the night. Usually, when Josh is down here, they ask him if he is off yet. Do they do that for me? No...that pissed me off...So right now, I don't really care much for anything, grated a small bit of people are going to get gifts from me, but thats not the point. Wrapping it up now, I just basically want to say that, if I start acting like I hate the world, chances are I do, but I'll never hate my self.

Oh, yeah...merry christmas and stuff...

"'And so the light will hide the evil of the world from beond.' You are a fool to challange the might of an angel."
In the blink of an eye, Trilmik had his sword through Aiedail's cheast. She had a surprzed looked on her face, and then she went limp. There was a scream of pain eminating all arounf them, but it wasn't coming from Aiedail. Trilmik pulled his sword from Aiedail's cheast, and she fell to the floor. Not one drop of blood had spilled, and not a silgle cut was on Aiedail's body. Both Trilmik's m\wings and sword faded away, and Trilmik picked up his old sword. He then walked into the next room, leaving Ethriden with an unconcious Aiedail.



Fellor looked at the group.
"I have my ways of getting around. What I mean when I say darkness does not always hide evil, is simply that. One vampire hidden in the shadow of a fallen kingdom, not harming any one and staying to him self, is nothing like the man who sits in a throne, surrounded by human guards, and trys to rule the world. Before raising the sword of destroction, thy lifting the glass of peace."



Shib woke up. She slowly opened her eyes and looked around. She was no longer in the clearing where she fought the shadow, but she was in a cave. Trilmik was walking towards her, a smaile spreading across his face.
"I would get up," She said, "but it would seem I can't."
Trilmik bent over and picked her up. He then sat down and started sinnging a relaxing lulaby. Slowly, Shib fell into a deep and peaceful sleep.



Asdreal stabbed the last man, and watched him fall. A total of twenty men. He then turned to look at the king.
"You're- You're suppose to be dead. I killed your family and freinds, how didn't you excape?!"
"I didn't, it would seem your guards just don't know how to kill small children. Me and my brother are the only Shape Shifteres left in the world. We are the last. You tried to kill us all, yet a small boy of nine sliped from your grasp. I am here now, and I am ready to here your reason."
"My reason? You want a reason for me killing you- you Monsters! I had no reason. You [i]things[/i] just had no right to live. You didn'r have a true from, you just borrowed those of others. I killed you to end that mokery of existence."
Asreal walked up to the king, leaned up close to his face and said, "I am not the monster in this room."
He then stbbed his sword into the kings gut, and pushed till it came out the top of his back. the king slumped over, and Asreal removed his sword.
"Long live the king..."
Asreal then morphed into a raven, and flew out the window. He was done killing for now, he wanted peace.

It bad when things start crashing down on your head...its worse when you find out its your fault...my writing is the only thing keeping me together, and eve that its doing it porly...I feel no one appreciates me...I work hard and I try hard, and people expect more from me...I fell lost, lonly...I feel like something is missing, or that I just don't belong...I have a hard time sleeping at night because I can't find a purpose...The reason for living is gone...I only keep my self going because thats all I have left...I feel the only reason to live is simply that...to live...people say hey care, yet when I start to talk, they leave...Evey one is too busy to care...christmas is here, and there are a few people that will get presents from me...I hope they don't think its just because their friends...friends...what are friends...people who make you happy? Then most of the world could be "friends"...why do people only care for themselves...no one seems to care what happens to others, just if it effects them...the world is a selfish, corrupt place...People tell me that I'm stupid...That I'm too young to know...If I'm too young, then why do I have a much better picture of life?...Things don't add up...and they probably never will...
Woo, its thanksgiving...well, that all I have to say...

The rain had just started.

      Clyde stood under the awning to his store. He made the mistake of wearing his Fedora today, the rain will ruin it. Clyde was average hight. He had brown hair and light skin. He dressed darkly which was why he was rather pale. But nether his clothes nor his skin was what bothered people, it was his blood red eyes.
      He has been told that they are completely normal, they just don't understand. He was born with his eyes, and so his parents were scared he was sick. No disease explained it, so they just tried to hide it. First they tried fake contacts. The color seemed to seep through them. Then they tried surgery, they would inject a color in to his eyes to change the color he had, nothing changed. Finally his dad got sick of it and decided, against the thoughts of any one else, to burn Clyde's eyes out and claim he was blind from birth. Thats when he ran.
      Clyde was only eleven when he ran from home. He was picked up by a young woman that cared for him. The one day she was in a terrible accident, and died.
      Thinking about that day he heard the news put tears in his eyes, or would have if that was possible. In the inside he cried, on the outside, he stared blankly at the sky. It rained harder.
      Clyde was startled from his thinking by a elderly woman standing next to him.
  "Are you ok young man?" She asked.
  "Yes, I'm fine...What are you doing here? This is an awful place to take a walk because of all the traffic, and there are no apartments for a mile around."
  "I seem to have miss placed my car..." She claimed as she looked around.
      Clyde looked at his pocket watch, eleven-o-clock. Something was not right, His store was the last to close around here, and that was half an hour ago. Clyde then noticed the woman was not wet.
  "Do you need a ride?" Clyde asked her.
  "No, it is around here some where."
  "Why are you not wet?"
      She simply said umbrella and showed him a black umbrella that she was holding. one problem, it was not wet ether. Clyde became slightly frightened. 
      Just then a car stopped at the streetlight across the road from them, the lights of the car blinding him. He turned his head toward the wall, looking at the light against it. One shadow, he saw this right when he realized a very scary thing, it was not his own.
      The woman smiled at him, turned, and walked into the rain. The rain never touched her. Then she vanished. When The old woman vanished, so did the car across the street. Somehow, two worlds exactly alike, for a few seconds, appeared to those blood red eyes.

      They say that one never really knows whats real and whats not, little do they know how right they are.
